<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= guild.name %> - Dashboard</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
</head>
<body>
  <main class="container">
    <h1><%= guild.name %></h1>
    <p>Configure key modules:</p>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>Quick Config</h2>
      <p>Use slash commands for full setup while dashboard MVP is active.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Moderation roles: <code>/setuproles</code></li>
        <li>Automod: <code>/automod</code></li>
        <li>Logging: <code>/logging setup</code></li>
        <li>Tickets: <code>/ticket-setup</code></li>
        <li>Starboard: <code>/starboard setup</code></li>
        <li>Welcomer: <code>/welcomer setup</code></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <a class="btn" href="/dashboard">Back to servers</a>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
